          <title>Supreme Court won&#8217;t take up fight over Pennsylvania mail ballot date requirement</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The Supreme Court said Tuesday it won’t hear civil rights groups’ appeal seeking to invalidate Pennsylvania's dating requirement for mail ballots, which has invalidated thousands of votes each recent election and become a central legal fight over voting in the key swing state.]]></description>
